'''Ivan Garczynski''' wrote "[[The Evacuation of Jatee]]," a roleplaying adventure that was published in [[West End Games]]' [[Supernova (WEG)|''Supernova'']]. In it he created the character Dr. [[Soron Hegerty]], who has since been included in the [[Force Heretic trilogy|''Force Heretic'' trilogy]] of [[Star Wars: The New Jedi Order|The New Jedi Order]] novels.

Ivan is also credited as an adviser in ''[[Planet of the Mists]]'' and [[Star Wars: The Roleplaying Game, Second Edition]]. His review of ''[[Survivor's Quest]]'' was posted on [[StarWars.com]] despite not being very flattering.

His alias is Been L'toth on [[Wookieepedia]].

